程序包的使用
xyz.noark.asm

  • 使用xyz.noark.asm的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    xyz.noark.asm
    这个包里的东东，其实就是ASM官方的类库。
    xyz.noark.asm.commons
    Provides some useful class and method adapters.
    xyz.noark.asm.tree
    Provides an ASM visitor that constructs a tree representation of the classes it visits.
    xyz.noark.asm.tree.analysis
    Provides a framework for static code analysis based on the asm.tree package.
    xyz.noark.asm.util
    Provides ASM visitors that can be useful for programming and debugging purposes.
    xyz.noark.asm.xml
    Provides SAX 2.0 adapters for ASM visitors to convert classes to and from XML.

    类和说明
    AnnotationVisitor
    A visitor to visit a Java annotation.
    Attribute
    A non standard class, field, method or code attribute.
    ByteVector
    A dynamically extensible vector of bytes.
    ClassReader
    A Java class parser to make a ClassVisitor visit an existing class.
    ClassVisitor
    A visitor to visit a Java class.
    FieldVisitor
    A visitor to visit a Java field.
    Handle
    A reference to a field or a method.
    Label
    A label represents a position in the bytecode of a method.
    MethodVisitor
    A visitor to visit a Java method.
    Type
    A Java field or method type.
    TypePath
    The path to a type argument, wildcard bound, array element type, or static inner type within an enclosing type.
    TypeReference
    A reference to a type appearing in a class, field or method declaration, or on an instruction.
